<body lang=EN-US>

<div class=WordSection1>

<h1>One More Thing &minus; Configure the solution:</h1>

<p class=MsoNormal>Your job had a failed vertex that has been downloaded and recreated locally.</p>

<p class=MsoNormal>The loaded assemblies do not yet contain your source code. Please follow these steps to add your project code to the debug solution:</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='text-indent:-.25in'>1.<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b><i>Right
click the Solution &gt; Add &gt; Existing Project</i></b> to add your
assemblies’ source code to the debugging solution.</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='text-indent:-.25in'>2.<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b><i>Right
click your source code project &gt; Properties &gt; Build</i></b> tab, set the
Output path as FailedVertexDebugHost working directory.</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast>(You can get the working directory through
right click FailedVertexDebugHost &gt; Properties.)</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><img width=625 height=373 id="Picture 2"
src="..\FvdSetOutputPath.png"></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

<h1>After configuring:</h1>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='text-indent:-.25in'>-<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>Press <b><i>F5</i></b> to run and debug the failed vertex.</p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='text-indent:-.25in'>-<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>Open up your code in the Solution Explorer and set breakpoints like you do with other c# projects.</p>


<p class=MsoNormal>To break when the failure occurs, please set CLR exceptions to break when thrown; otherwise, the vertex will catch and handle the exception. You can set this by checking <b>Common Language Runtime Exceptions</b>
in Debug &gt; Windows &gt; Exception Settings (Ctrl + Alt + E).</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><img width=452 height=235 id="Picture 3"
src="..\FvdExceptionSettings.png"></p>

<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;</p>

</div>

</body>

